If I had a waterproof camera, the top 5 things that I would want to photograph would be:

1) Underwater Rock Concert
2) Underwater/Under the pool (with a glass floor) Club Scene
3) The beautiful ocean floor and corals of the Philippine Beaches
4) A magnificent wakeboarding trick - First-person View
5) A lightning shot in the middle of a storm (perhaps with a couple on the foreground?)

Hahaha.

Imagine. These are the perfect locations wherein you can use this type of camera to it's full extent. Best advertising commercial ideas as well if you ask me.

Wouldn't you agree?


- Mike G. Navarrete

Wala akong makita sa hinaharap

Silipin ang iyong kahapon
Doon nakabaon

Iniwan mo ang iyong pangako
Minsan lang totoo

Sa labas ako nag aabang
Naghihintay - nagpapalipas na ng oras na
Hindi na babalik
Hindi na darating ang minimithi

Sa iyo ang dasal
Sa akin ang gawa

Iniwan mo ang iyong pangako
Minsan lang totoo

Sa iyo ang dasal
Sa iyo ang gawa
Gawa na ang lahat
Nasaan ka na?

Iniwan mo ang iyong pangako
Minsan lang totoo

Minsan lang.

Amp.. Haha.. Talaga lang ah..=p ------------------- Anyway, first of summer, and I'm really really bored. Fixed the room kanina, pero yun lang. Waah! Need to go out. Guys.. Miss ko na kaagad kayo!>< Swerte nga pala mga nag-bora, congrats. Hehe.. Yun lang.. Ingat.

Today was D-Day.. Graduation. The end of it all..

13 friggin years ended today.. Grabe ang supot ng loyalty award.. WE WERE SUPPOSED TO RECEIVE MEDALS!! PWEH!!><

I'd write a long entry with tributes and all, but I'm too lazy and/or tired.. Haha..>< So maybe saka nalang..

Basta as of now, all I can say is..

<font size = 36 color = blue>
CONGRATULATIONS BATCH 'O6!! THE TRUE STAR BATCH!!
</font>


Hehe..

We are really going to be the makers of the greatest story ever told.

Ingat kayo lahat.. I'm gonna miss you guys.. Hehe.. Kita-kita nalang lagi!

Saludo.

Woke up early today coz I had to proxy for my Kuya sa Baptism.. Yeah.. First time ako pumasok ng Protestant church.. Walang mga candle or water or whatever yung Baptism.. Wala lang.. Then Reception sa bahay ng Kuya Eyo (Dad ng baby, si Gabe).. Hehe.. Daming food.. Tas laftrip.. Tas karaoke pa.. Saya talaga ng tropang Banalo.. Hehe.. Basta yun.. Tas pag punta ko sa mga nanay (lola), ang dami ding food.. Tapos pag uwi ko.. ang dami ding food! Waah!! Hehe..>< Basta solid foodtrip. Hehe.. Anyway.. Grabe.. 3 school days left. Shit.. Senior year has come and gone too fast..>< Guys.. Seryoso, this is the time na kailangan natin sagad-sagarin lahat ng kaya natin gawin.. Haha.. To those included: Chili Challenge natin! Haha.. Yeah.. Ano pa mga kailangan gawin? Badtrip I think ang dami kong namiss sa school kasi 1 week kaming off..>< Waah.. Final Finals pa naman.. Waah.. Need to catch up.. Need to pass.. Hehe.. I hate Math..>< Hassle.. Ingat.

Wala lang..

Gusto ko lang mag update.. Hehe..

Tinatamad ako magkwento eh.. hehe.. ><

Magluluto ako ng dinner namin tomorrow.. Chicken Pasta (Fra Diablo), and the 'Mongolian' rice ko na hindi, tapos steak. Hehe.. Hassle ako bukas ah.. 

Uhm..

What else?

Malapit na mag Christmas.. But ewan.. I don't really feel it or something.. =/

Bahala na..


Ingat.
